transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. This is Olivia speaking. Who do I have the pleasure of speaking with today?

Speaker 2: Hi. My name is Rogelio Gomez. I just received a product from you guys, and it says generic Viagra. You guys, you just said Viagra. Is this legitimately Viagra? Is this a generic version?

Speaker 1: Yeah. I can look into this for you. Okay. Rogelio, what is your date of birth?

Speaker 2: 11-23-77.

Speaker 1: Okay, great. And are you located at 220 Rebecca Lane, Arcata, California, 95521?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Yeah. So I do see your prescription here. Okay. So you said you received the generic. Is that right?

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: The regular generic?

Speaker 2: Yeah. That's not what I was told that it would be.

Speaker 1: Okay. So you are looking for the AGV. Is that right?

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: Okay. Yeah. So I will ship you out the AGV on us then since you did already pay for it.

Speaker 2: Can I just confirm that your address or the address to send it to is 220 Rebecca Lane, Arcata, California, 95521?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: Okay, great. So you should receive this within the next two to five business days, probably by next Wednesday, but you know the winter storm is crazy. So I would say maybe next Friday at the latest. And this will definitely be the AGV. And the way that you will know is the pills on them, they will say 50450. The regular generic pills, they just say something like AC340 on them. These will just say the numbers of the milligrams, 50. And then the side of the bottle should say Greenstone because that's the manufacturer, and AGV.

Speaker 1: And as long as you take them on an empty stomach and without alcohol, you will definitely notice a significant improvement compared to the regular Viagra. So yeah, I am really sorry about that, but I did ship you out the replacement and you should receive it soon.

Speaker 2: Okay. What should I do with these ones?

Speaker 1: Oh, whatever you want. You can throw them away. You can use them. It's up to you.

Speaker 2: Okay. What kind of effect will they have?

Speaker 1: You know, they're still FDA approved third-party tested Viagra, just not as significant or as potent an impact as the AGV.

Speaker 2: Okay. Okay. Thank you.

Speaker 1: Yeah, thank you.

Speaker 2: And how many would you be sending? How many would we be getting?

Speaker 1: The same amount, 10.

Speaker 2: Okay. Okay. Thank you.

Speaker 1: Thank you. I hope you have a great day.

Speaker 2: You too. Bye-bye.

Speaker 1: Okay. Bye.
